    align:confidence "0.85"^^xsd:float ;
    align:rationale "Both concepts define 'Modality' as the form of an AI system. While the AIDOC definition is more detailed and explicitly mentions controlled vocabularies for enumeration/reuse – suggesting a focus on practical implementation and standardization – the core meaning aligns closely with the airo concept’s simpler description. They aren't *exactly* interchangeable due to this difference in detail, but are very similar."^^xsd:string ;
    align:relation skos:closeMatch ;
    align:source aidoc:Modality ;
    align:target <https://w3id.org/airo#Modality> .

